data.text:
Our Team is small, Our Network is Powerful

Working with a diverse selection of clients across the Music, Art, Fashion and Culture sectors Neighbourhood has grown into group of companies with a deep range of expertise.

We pride ourselves on our ability to understand many areas of our clients business and are ready to help them break convention and ignite positive conversations.

At the core, Neighbourhood delivers strategic and creative communications, marketing, content and public relations in the fields of music, culture, fashion and entertainment yet extends to cover innovation, investment, and live.
